OL,3,C'The sounds my children make are
OL,4,Cliterally crucifying for me'
OL,6,F"I miss talking to my children, I miss
OL,7,Fbeing outside, I miss laughter, I miss
OL,8,Fdoing the school run, I miss being
OL,9,Fpart of our family," Karen said.
OL,11,F"Even the sound of their laughter is
OL,12,Ftorturous to me. Everything has to be
OL,13,Fkept to the minimal because the sound
OL,14,Fthat they make are literally
OL,15,Fcrucifying for me, it's torture."
OL,17,FKaren was diagnosed with a condition
OL,18,Fcalled Pain Hyperacusis in 2022, but
OL,19,Fnot much is known about how to treat
OL,20,Fit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
