OL,3,C'The sounds my children make are
OL,4,Cliterally crucifying for me'
OL,6,FDespite making herself partially deaf
OL,7,Fin one ear - she is yet to find
OL,8,Fanything that helps.
OL,10,FWhat is Hyperacusis?
OL,12,FKaren's form of Hyperacusis means that
OL,13,Fany noise is agony.
OL,15,F"The pain from sound is in my ears
OL,16,Flike an earache, like a constant
OL,17,Fearache that just doesn't stop," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
