OL,3,C'The sounds my children make are
OL,4,Cliterally crucifying for me'
OL,6,F"Like a deep burning pain and then the
OL,7,Fpain spreads across the scalp, pain
OL,8,Fand pressure in my face, pain in my
OL,9,Fteeth and in the roof of my mouth."
OL,11,FHer condition is also accompanied by
OL,12,Fsevere reactive tinnitus.
OL,14,F"I've got several different sounds, it
OL,15,Fsounds like a hoover and like a siren
OL,16,Fin my head."
OL,18,FKaren wears earplugs and defenders 24-
OL,19,F7, even when she is at home alone and
OL,20,Fthe only way she now communicates is
OL,21,Fthrough whispers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
