OL,3,C'The sounds my children make are
OL,4,Cliterally crucifying for me'
OL,6,F"I only keep going because i've got
OL,7,Fchildren, because I really wouldn't
OL,8,Fotherwise," she added.
OL,10,FKaren's partner Nick says that the
OL,11,Fimpact that her condition has had on
OL,12,Fthe family is "massive".
OL,14,FNick said: "It has totally changed
OL,15,Feverything we've known as a family to
OL,16,Fbe honest.
OL,18,F"Before, we were out at any given
OL,19,Fopportunity, like holidays, we can't
OL,20,Fdo anything that we used to.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
