OL,3,C'The sounds my children make are
OL,4,Cliterally crucifying for me'
OL,6,F"But she wants to be involved, she
OL,7,Fwants to feel like she is still apart
OL,8,Fof the family."
OL,10,FKaren spends Christmas and birthdays
OL,11,Fin the conservatory of her home,
OL,12,Flooking through the window as she
OL,13,Fwatches the family unwrap their
OL,14,Fpresents in the front room.
OL,16,F"They'll bring them to the window and
OL,17,Fthey'll show me their presents," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
