OL,3,C'The sounds my children make are
OL,4,Cliterally crucifying for me'
OL,6,F"And on their birthdays, I watch them
OL,7,Fwith their friends in the garden. I'm
OL,8,Fliterally a spectator on their lives."
OL,10,FThe NHS says reintroducing sounds like
OL,11,Fwhite noise can help build back
OL,12,Ftolerance for some with the condition.
OL,13,FBut for others like Karen, there's
OL,14,Fvery little treatment that provides
OL,15,Frelief.
OL,17,FKen Devore, from Hyperacusis Research,
OL,18,Fsaid: "There really is no effective
OL,19,Ftreatment for hyperacusis, certainly
OL,20,Ffor any type of severe Hyperacusis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
