OL,3,C'The sounds my children make are
OL,4,Cliterally crucifying for me'
OL,6,F"Sound therapy can potentially trigger
OL,7,Fsetbacks or cause a worsening."
OL,9,FDespite having experimental surgery in
OL,10,F2024 which made her partially deaf in
OL,11,Fone ear, it did not work.
OL,13,FShe is now preparing to undergo
OL,14,Fexperimental surgery to implant a high
OL,15,Fcervical spinal cord simulator, a tens-
OL,16,Flike machine, under her skin and
OL,17,Fattached to the cranial nerves in her
OL,18,Fspine, with the hope of disrupting the
OL,19,Fsignals from her ears to her brain.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
