OL,3,C'The sounds my children make are
OL,4,Cliterally crucifying for me'
OL,6,FKaren said: "I will try anything to
OL,7,Fget a quality of life back to the
OL,8,Fchildren. I will try anything to get
OL,9,Fback to them.
OL,11,F"Because i'm at a level where I am
OL,12,Fincompatible with life, I can't
OL,13,Fenvisage 30 years of it. living in a
OL,14,Froom in silence is absolute torture.
OL,16,F"We need the medical community to hear
OL,17,Fus and to at least try things, because
OL,18,Fliving like this isn't an option.
OL,19,FThere's so many of us and we need
OL,20,Fhelp, experimental treatments to be
OL,21,Ftrialled, or nothing ever changes."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
